Re: ProMED-mail Chickenpox, children - India: (AS) 20110511.1453
----------------------------------------------------------------
Although chickenpox vaccine (both Sanofi and GSK products) is
available and very popular in the private sector medical practice, it
is not included in the national immunisation program in India.

